        TradeResult trade​(HashMap<String,​Coin> interestedCoins)
        Perform a trade given a collection of coins and their info.
        Parameters:
        interestedCoins - a mapping from a coin's ticker symbol (e.g. BTC) to its coin info
        Returns:
        TradeResult, either a successful trade result or a null trade result if the trade was unsuccessful
